data.description: WELCOME HOME to this beautifully unique, 5 bed, 3.5 bath custom colonial home on one of the level lots in Aquia Harbour. Built by the builder for the builder with no expense spared. This home features many efficiency upgrades including 2x6 exterior walls (huge energy savings), a newly completed basement remodel by HIVEX that includes a full bathroom, 5th bedroom, family room, dining area, kitchenette, bonus room, additional storage areas, and a perimeter drainage management system. Open and inviting floor plan ideally designed with entertaining your guests in mind. Upstairs features 4 spacious bedrooms, multiple full bathrooms, laundry room with a custom stainless sink. The upgraded master bath with granite and tile throughout, an oversized lighted and jetted tub, separate tile shower, double vanity, walk-in closet. Roof, appliances, flooring throughout replaced circa 2018, main HVAC in 2016, and attic HVAC in 2011.
